summary: This mod attempts to make Illia more in tune with what I perceive as an attractive yet alternative looking young witch. This was a user request for a more Gothic looking Illia and I took his request from there. She is available in either Essential or Non-essential variations in a Calculated level 45 or Auto-Level from 10 to 85.  Happy Halloween!
